subject: Olympic Games (2008)
Track and Field
lead_paragraph: Alan Webb ran the night’s fastest time of 3 minutes 41.27 seconds, advancing easily to Friday’s semifinal round. But there remains much uncertainty about Webb’s chances of earning an Olympic spot.
